Questions:
What alternative treatment options are available to you if you decide not to participate in the telephone-based intervention study for Hispanic cancer survivors with anxiety and/or depression?
A) You can choose to have no treatment at all for your symptoms;
B) You can seek treatment from a community provider outside of the study;
C) You will be automatically enrolled in a different research study;
D) You will receive a self-help book on managing anxiety and depression without any guidance.

Correct answer: B
